  "3108990": {
    "name": "蝶梦",
    "steam_appid": 3108990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手持变形斩武器，还会枪反、弹反、盾反的白发小姐姐！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终极精品版本已上线！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还不快试一试吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br><strong>《蝶梦》是一款小型复古类魂游戏。在回归传统箱庭式关卡探索和战斗体验的基础上，在游戏中融入道家庄周梦蝶的典故，以及佛家《金刚经》的元素。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>在一个叫做法尔戈迪亚的国度，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唤蝶仪式的古老咒语再次唤醒了沉睡的宿命， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这片土地的王，维纶拜尔，已然蜕变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维纶拜尔与蝶的相遇，是宿命的枷锁？是罪业的轮回？还是对存在意义的探索？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将“梦”到自己成为“蝶”，揭开这一切的来龙去脉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【复古箱庭式关卡】</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“凡所有相，皆为虚妄”</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >误入诡异的梦境，探索黑暗的中世纪古堡，沉浸在魔幻的神秘氛围中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入危机四伏的世界，破解错综复杂的箱庭地图。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找多样的武器道具，战胜阻碍你的强大怪物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/ec55f4b1f7ef9f63b462cdf14177ea3e.poster.avif?t=1772085496\" width=560 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/ec55f4b1f7ef9f63b462cdf14177ea3e.webm?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/ec55f4b1f7ef9f63b462cdf14177ea3e.mp4?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【经典碎片化叙事】</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“曾经有一个人，他梦见自己成了蝴蝶”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以人物对话，道具收集为线索，在迷茫中拼凑出梦境的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验欲望的放大和扭曲，感受人成为怪物的挣扎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/402e6db069da0eaa52cf4bce7b40de93.poster.avif?t=1772085496\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/402e6db069da0eaa52cf4bce7b40de93.webm?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/402e6db069da0eaa52cf4bce7b40de93.mp4?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【高自由度的战斗】</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“求祢的宝血洗净我们，赦免我们一切的罪”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战黑暗腐蚀的敌人，唤醒沉寂的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独具特色的武器装备，由“蝶刃”衍生出的多种战斗方式，选择你擅长的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合传统魂系战斗的弹反、枪反等机制，多变的应对策略，带给你一场酣畅淋漓的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/f61d10aa36d7f56fa42ef0335d72829e.poster.avif?t=1772085496\" width=642 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/f61d10aa36d7f56fa42ef0335d72829e.webm?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/f61d10aa36d7f56fa42ef0335d72829e.mp4?t=1772085496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>QQ群：887425142<br>官方微信:LiberFish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:邮箱：hddy2000@qq.com\">邮箱：hddy2000@qq.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摩点网众筹ID：138621</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>感谢所有参与众筹，帮助我们完成本游戏的188名玩家！</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小黑盒二维码：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108990/extras/bb3cfb791b6c739c3e672444b99ecad8.avif?t=1772085496\" width=1530 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>以下是推荐的图形设置（参考系均为1920×1080p，60FPS稳定运行）：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于NVIDIA GTX 1650/RTX 2050或同等性能显卡：推荐使用低画质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于RTX 3060/RTX 3070（我们标注为推荐）或同等性能显卡：推荐使用中等画质（我们的默认设置）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于3080或更高性能显卡：推荐使用高画质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他关于配置：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的中等画质是定制的，目的是尽量不损失太多与高画质相比的游戏体验，同时确保帧率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于更高性能的显卡，我们自己的数据显示，在3090ti上，目前在2K超高画质下平均帧率为50fps。请将此作为参考。我们仍在努力将此帧率提高到60fps。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若PC配置太低可能帧数不足，游玩起来会不流畅。进入游戏后，按Tab键将能实时开关内置的游戏帧数查看面板。若您购买后发现任何bug、掉帧等问题，可通过邮箱与我们联系，我们承诺一定会予以解决。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外注意：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、demo版本略早于正式版，存档不可继承至正式版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、若游戏中遇到提灯消失的情况，请保存游戏重新进入即可恢复正常。（此bug制作组复现概率极低，目前制作组正全力复现和修复。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于AI使用：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内某些声音、建模等可能由AI生成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>",
